  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>The convention for multi-line git commit messages is to separate a longer
message body from the short description with an empty line. (Apparently so that
some tools in the real world do not get confused)
It would look way prettier if the commit message for the git mission followed
that convention.</pre>
   </td>
